name: Life Full of Beauty
description:
Happiness can be created by our self. life is full of beauty. from something simple, to see flowers, enjoy the colors, smell the rain and feel the wind, it creates a taste. Succulent flower become a symbol of beauty in this artwork, succulent flower have a long life. This flower represents in savoring the beauty that exists in life. Simple happiness i can feel when i look at flowers. There is so much beauty and godness around us that we can be grateful and happy.

Aol.

watercolor on a3 paper
3507x4960 pixels
300 dpi
